parameters: \n<Ameria>"Lack of sleep? Couldn't you fall asleep?"

\n<Lyric>"Yeah... someone kept clinging to me, made it impossible to
get comfortable."
\n<Roselitte>"...Well then. Both of you, are you ready?"

\n<Roselitte>"First, as planned, we'll investigate the thieves connected
to Lord Anatos."

\n<Roselitte>"I've already asked the soldiers here to check the
investigation records around Anatos. They should bring us
information about the thieves soon."

\n<Roselitte>"In the meantime, while we wait, shall we head to the
'refugee camp' in this town? Along with gathering
information, let's check on the condition of the people who
have taken refuge."
\n<Ameria>"Yeah, I agree. Where is the refugee camp located?"
\n<Roselitte>"It seems they've made the town square into a campsite."

\n<Ameria>"The town square... So it's to the west from here, right?
That place is indeed spacious, might be a good spot for
refuge."
\n<Lyric>"Hmm, you're quite familiar with this town, aren't you?"

\n<Ameria>"Well, I used to live here... though it was quite some time
ago."
\n<Lyric>"Is that so? I thought you'd always been in Abel."

\n<Ameria>"Yeah... There were some complications, and I got injured.
That's when a priest took me in, and after that, I moved to
Abel."
\n<Roselitte>"...Alright, are we all set? Let's depart."
